module.name: weather
module.description: A module that provides current weather data based on location, or configured location. If no location is provided, respond with 'No Location' as the argument.
module.argument: Location (City, Zip, Lat/Lon, etc.) / Or 'None' if not specified.

embeddings.text: Check the current temperature in your location using a weather app.
Find out the weather forecast for the next 5 days using a weather website.
Determine the chance of precipitation in your area for the next 24 hours using a weather app or website.
Check the wind speed and direction in your location using a weather app or website.
Determine the UV index in your area using a weather app or website.
Find out if there are any severe weather alerts or warnings in your area using a weather app or website.
